product_name: L'OrealParadise Big Deal Volumizing and Lengthening Washable Mascara
summary: SummaryMake your lashes a Big Deal! L'Oréal Paris Paradise Big Deal Volumizing and Lengthening Washable Mascara delivers endless volume & length. Clump-free, buildable formula
details: DetailsFeaturesMake your lashes a Big Deal with endlessly buildable volume and lengthClump resistant lashes, no matter how much you layerInfused with New Self-Smoothing Complex that smooths lashes with each layer for lightweight, continuously buildable impactUnique cross-conic brush evenly coats lashes with every stroke while separating and extending lashes for a clump-resistant resultBenefitsSuitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearersRemoves with ease!Item 2633453How To UsePlace cross conic brush at the base of lashes and gently sweep up to tip. Repeat to build endless volume and length.IngredientsAqua / Water / Eau, Behenyl Behenate, Acrylates Copolymer, Cetearyl Alcohol, Stearic Acid, Palmitic Acid, Poly C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate, Butylene Glycol, PVP, VP/Eicosene Copolymer, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Kaolin, Phenoxyethanol, Caprylyl Glycol, Pentylene Glycol, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, Myristic Acid . May Contain: CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / Iron Oxides. (F.I.L. N70052177/1).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsShipping Restrictions : This item cannot be shipped via air.
how_to_use: Place cross conic brush at the base of lashes and gently sweep up to tip. Repeat to build endless volume and length.

reviews.headline: Did the job
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Packaged well and is good value for money. Did not cover my eyelashes as well as i would've liked to be dark and long but didn't do a horrible job either.

reviews.headline: Love the brush and formula
reviews.comments: I bought the original Lash Paradise mascara which I wasn't a big fan of but this one is great. The brush is perfect for a clump free experience. The tube doesn't dispense too much product (it was slightly too wet in the first use but was perfect from the second use onwards). It doesn't flake on me. I bought the shade blackest black.

reviews.headline: Lifts, separates, and defines—no smudging, no fallout, just
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This mascara is everything! The formula is rich and the color is bold—my lashes looked longer, fuller, and beautifully separated. The brush is pure magic: it glides through easily with zero pulling or clumping, and I didn't get any smudges on my eyelids while applying. Best part? No fallout under my eyes, even after a long day. It seriously made my lashes look like falsies without the hassle. A solid 100/10 in my book!

reviews.headline: The best mascara!
reviews.comments: I have really small lashes & this the best mascara I've tried. It doesn't clump.

reviews.headline: Decent
reviews.comments: This mascara is good for the price, it lengthens my lashes and gives some volume, but unfortunately it smudges so easily. I would repurchase it but it smudges and gives me racoon eyes so I will not be buying this again.

reviews.headline: Nothing Great
reviews.comments: Its the same mascara formula as the original paradise mascara with a differnt wand. It didnt really do anything special for my lashes. Its ok if you want a drug store product.

reviews.headline: Great!

I do think that if you let it dry in between coats, it gets a bit better but this one was just not as good as the other L'Oreal mascara

reviews.comments: I really love the way this mascara brought volume and length to my lashes. I needed a break for cluster lashes and this mascara makes me feel like I'm not missing any lashes.

faceoff_positive.comments:
The L'Oreal Paris Big Deal Mascara is exactly that—a big deal! I've tried countless mascaras, but this one genuinely stands out. From the moment I applied it, I noticed how effortlessly it lifted, lengthened, and volumized my lashes. The brush is the perfect size, coating every lash evenly without clumping. Plus, the formula is lightweight, buildable, and lasts all day without flaking or smudging—even through humid weather or long workdays.

What I love most is how it gives that false-lash effect while still looking natural and fluttery. Whether you're going for a subtle daytime look or bold, dramatic lashes for a night out, this mascara delivers every time. And let's not forget the sleek packaging—it's such a luxe touch for an affordable product!

If you're on the hunt for a mascara that truly delivers on its promises, this is the one. faceoff_positive.headline: YES

faceoff_negative.comments: I like the original Lash Paradise formula much better. This new Paradise Big Deal mascara made my eyes burn, both when applying and after removal at the end of the day. It also clumped my lashes together because the brush bristles are too far apart to be able to effectively separate your lashes. This also flaked after the first use. I expect a mascara to flake once it is older and has been open for a while (that's when I usually decide to replace mine), but I don't think a brand-new mascara should be flaking already! For the price, I could buy a mini prestige brand mascara that is better quality. I would not purchase this again.
faceoff_negative.headline: Original Lash Paradise is better
